### Task Management API - Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5083
@httpsUrl = https://localhost:7191

### 1. Get all tasks (should be empty initially)
GET {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Create a new task with title and description
POST {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the Task Management API"
}

###

### 3. Create another task (title only)
POST {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Review pull requests"
}

###

### 4. Create a third task
POST {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Fix bugs in authentication module",
  "description": "Address the issues reported in tickets #101 and #102"
}

###

### 5. Get all tasks (should now have tasks)
GET {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get a specific task by ID (replace {id} with actual ID, e.g., 1)
GET {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Mark a task as complete (replace {id} with actual ID)
PUT {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/1/complete

###

### 8. Get the completed task to verify
GET {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Delete a task (replace {id} with actual ID)
DELETE {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/2

###

### 10. Try to get deleted task (should return 404)
GET {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Validation test - Create task without title (should fail)
POST {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This task has no title"
}

###

### 12. Validation test - Create task with empty title (should fail)
POST {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "This task has empty title"
}

###

### 13. Try to mark non-existent task as complete (should return 404)
PUT {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/9999/complete

###

### 14. Try to delete non-existent task (should return 404)
DELETE {{httpsUrl}}/api/tasks/9999

###

